longBusinessSummary: MAX 21 AG, a technology holding company, operates in the postal and mail management, IT security, and IT and cloud services sectors. The company offers printing management and postal distribution solutions, including solution for business communication, letter consolidation, and input/output management. It also offers login security and identity connection products; and provides consulting, support, hard/software, and other solutions, as well as LinOTP product suite, which is used for adaptive multi-factor authentication. The company was formerly known as MAX21 Management und Beteiligungen AG and changed its name to MAX 21 AG in September 2016. MAX 21 AG was founded in 2003 and is based in Weiterstadt, Germany.
